	<text>
		<body>
			<div type="transcription">
				<p>From: Minister <persName ref="#ehri_dr_masutani">Hideo Masutani</persName> (<placeName ref="#helsinki">Helsinki</placeName>)</p>
				<p>To: MOFA <persName ref="#ehri_dr_shigenori_togo">Togo Shigenori</persName> (<placeName ref="#tokyo">Tokyo</placeName>)</p>
				<p>Re: Conversation with <placeName ref="#slovak-republic">Slovakian</placeName> Minister about domestic affairs</p>
				<p>….</p>
				<p> 3. The issue of <term ref="#t864" type="subject">Jews</term> who have great influence in <term ref="#t816" type="subject"
						>economy</term> is an important <term ref="#t351?dlid=deu" type="subject">political issue</term>. Current cabinet minister and
					head of the <orgName ref="#g397">Hlinka Guard</orgName>
					<persName ref="#p000261">Sano Mach</persName> is using his skills to resolve it. </p>
			</div>
		</body>
